#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"A delicate blend of soft pink roses and baby's breath, perfect for "
"expressing love and gratitude."
msgstr ""
"Un mélange délicat de roses et de gypsophiles, idéal pour exprimer son amour "
"et son affection."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline Turner, Bouquet Designer"
msgstr "Aline Turner, Créatrice de bouquets"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline is the mastermind behind our bespoke floral arrangements."
msgstr "Aline est la créatrice de nos arrangements floraux sur mesure."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Bloom with Joy:"
msgstr "Bloom with Joy:"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Blushing Harmony"
msgstr "Blushing Harmony"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid ""
"Brighten any corner of the globe with our express 24-hour worldwide flower "
"delivery service."
msgstr ""
"Illuminez n'importe quel coin du monde avec notre service express de "
"livraison de fleurs dans le monde entier en 24 heures."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Bringing the Beauty of Nature to Your Space"
msgstr "Nous faisons entrer la beauté de la nature dans votre espace"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Celebrate with Our Best-Selling Bouquets, perfect for every occasion."
msgstr "Célébrez chaque occasion avec nos bouquets les plus vendus."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Discover Our Most Loved Arrangements"
msgstr "Découvrez nos compositions les plus appréciées"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_orchid.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nom d'affichage"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Elegant Simplicity"
msgstr "Une élégante simplicité"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Enhance your surroundings with our exquisite floral arrangements and garden "
"designs. We offer a variety of options that bring the serenity and beauty of "
"nature into your home or workspace."
msgstr ""
"Embellissez votre environnement avec nos arrangements floraux exquis et nos "
"conceptions de jardin. Nous offrons une variété d'options qui apportent la "
"sérénité et la beauté de la nature dans votre maison ou votre espace de "
"travail."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Explore Our Gardens"
msgstr "Découvrez nos jardins"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_title
msgid ""
"Explore our handcrafted floral arrangements, each meticulously designed to "
"convey beauty, elegance, and a touch of nature's artistry."
msgstr ""
"Découvrez nos compositions florales artisanales, conçues méticuleusement "
"pour transmettre la beauté, l'élégance et une touche artistique issue de la "
"nature."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Fresh Flowers Delivered to Your Doorstep!"
msgstr "Des fleurs fraîches livrées à domicile !"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid "Global 24-Hour Flower Delivery"
msgstr "Livraison de fleurs 24 heures sur 24"

